        @NotNull
List<SubstituteMenuItem> createItems​(@Nullable
                                     SubstituteMenuLookup menuLookup)
        Creates applicable menu items from the menus returned by menuLookup. If menuLookup is null, creates the default menu lookup.
        Parameters:
        menuLookup - a menu reference, may be null
        Returns:
        menu items for the node, not null but possibly empty
